Author: ckaiycool
Post: https://forum.gimx.fr/viewtopic.php?f=9&t=3626
Game: Sniper Elite 3
Platform: PS3
Device: Mouse/Keyboard
Playability: GOOD

Please read the notes below since this configuration has lots of different tweaks.

Profile 1 has stick intensity to walk or run while while staning up. (does not work while in crouch/ prone postition since that mode only has one speed.) Use Scroll wheel up to run and scroll wheel down to walk.
Profile 2 While aiming with scope aim mode, scroll wheel toggles zoom in/out.
Profile 3 The third profile has [Q] as a trigger button. This enables the mouse to be used when selecting weapons and other things in Radial Menu.
The 3rd profile was made because of the WAY different Dead zone setting compared to the other profiles. Dead Zone profile 1 and 2 = 15/ Profile 3 Dead zone = 64.
Profile 3 also has a different x/y ratio compared to profile 1 and 2.

Other notes:
Ingame settings aim assist OFF
Controls sensitivity x/y MAX
Scope Sensitivity x/y MAX
-->
